SUMMARY:Drop-in Drawing
DTSTAMP:20260327T071959Z
DTSTART:20260410T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Deepen your connection to art through the meditative act of dra
	wing! Every second Thursday\, the Frye galleries become a welcoming space 
	to drop-in\, slow down\, and draw inspiration from the works on view. Frye
	 teaching artists are present to support your drawing\, encourage close lo
	oking\, and help create a relaxed\, self-guided experience. Come solo or w
	ith a friend\; stay for fifteen minutes or settle in for the full session—
	the choice is yours. All skill levels are welcome\, and youth may particip
	ate with an accompanying adult. Materials are provided. --- https://fryemu
	seum.org/calendar/event/drop-in-drawing-2026\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.c
