BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:1Aw6EXk9rlS2LRjdb_Q29
SUMMARY:Rocketship\, The Telephone Numbers\, Remedy & Wren
DTSTAMP:20260327T071959Z
DTSTART:20260417T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $20 ($26.27 after fees)\n\nDay of: $25 ($31.42 after f
	ees)\n\nRocketship\n\n“A Certain Smile\, A Certain Sadness” 30th Anniversa
	ry Re-issue and West Coast Tour\n\nSome of the best records are those that
	 transcend the usual parameters of music to create worlds of their own. Wh
	en it’s clear that what you’re listening to isn’t just a collection of tha
	t year’s songs\, but a deeply thought-out\, architected space where ideas 
	clash\, converse\, interlock\; these are the albums that end up lasting we
	ll beyond their era\, changing with us\, and revealing new surprises every
	 time we return to them. One of the clearest examples of an album that cra
	fts a strange and beautiful world not quite like any other is Rocketship’s
	 1996 full-length debut A Certain Smile\, A Certain Sadness. Even upon arr
	ival\, this was an experience unto itself\, and 30 years later\, these eig
	ht songs of bittersweet bliss still feel new. Slumberland is delighted to 
	release a 30th Anniversary edition of this instant classic\, making it rea
	dily available on vinyl and CD once again after years of unavailability an
	d collector demand.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+ b
	ar and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://link.
	dice.fm/Uf56e9ad5693\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/Uf56e9ad5693
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
